{
  "stem": "18581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And afterwards, either the farmer was not happy to keep me, maybe he did not believe in my flimsy excuse, you know, that I was a Lithuanian from the area of Telz, I said, not from my hometown, and I was running away from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then alternatively I said I was looking for my parents that were expelled by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was looking-- I heard that they jumped the train in this area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after that, he put me to another farmer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other farmer was called Jakimavicius.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And would you spell the name of that farmer?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "J-A-K-I-M-A-V-I-C-I-U-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, after a while, the priest, when he visited me and discovered that I knew plenty about the Catholic religion, because sometimes I used to remain in class when they had religion classes.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have to go to the Jewish religion classes, because I was far ahead of-- of my teacher.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the rabbi's daughter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was more ahead because I-- for eight years, I had a permanent rabbi training me every day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I used to stay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew about the catechism.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew other things, so I used to teach catechism to daughters of Jakimavicius.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a Lithuanian and I taught them in Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What-- what-- But",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tried not to appear publicly and tried to keep to myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I understood that in case of a really big inquiry would be a problem.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was, of course, some doubt about my being a Lithuanian Catholic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is when the story with the pig came and actually helped me to establish myself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was invited to sviezines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That means fresh, fresh blood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you do it by stabbing a pig and drinking its hot, gushing blood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sviezines.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "S-V-I-E-Z-I-N-E-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
